To reproduce:
1) Set up Eucalyptus 4.0.1 Cloud
2) Create account, group and user using euare commands
3) Use euare-groupupload-policy with the policy file attached:
{code}
[root@odc-f-13 ~]# euare-groupuploadpolicy -g user02 -p describe-instances -f describe-instances.json --region account1-user01@
euare-groupuploadpolicy: error (MalformedPolicyDocument): Error in uploaded policy: {
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Action": [
        "ec2:DescribeInstances"
      ],
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Resource": "arn:aws:ec2:*:408396244283:instance/*"
    }
  ]
}
{code}

[~hspencer] I am not able to reproduce this issue with the provided euare-groupupload-policy. I am not seeing the the error :
{code}
 net.sf.json.JSONException: 'arn:aws:ec2:*:408396244283:instance/*' is not a valid ARN 
{code}

This what I am seeing in 4.1
{code}
[c-21:~]euare-groupuploadpolicy -g test-group -p describe-instances -f role-describe-instances-v2.json --region test-account-test-user@
[c-21:~]euare-grouplistpolicies -g test-group
describe-instances
{code}
